%% Diagram: Variable-height measurement and correction flow
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant V as Virtualizer
    participant C as Cache
    participant D as DOM+RO

    U->>V: scroll (rAF)
    V->>C: lookup heights
    C-->>V: measured + est.
    V->>D: render window
    D-->>V: RO: actual heights
    V->>C: write measured
    V->>V: recompute total
    Note over V,D: Wrong est. → jump.<br/>Overscan + anchor mitigate.
